'''Casino de Port-Gentil''' is a [[casino]] in [[Port-Gentil]], [[Gabon]]. It is located just north of [[Saint Louis Church, Port-Gentil|Saint Louis Church]] and the [[École Mixte]].<ref name="GM">{{cite map|title=[[Google Maps]]|publisher=Google|accessdate=10 March 2011}}</ref> The casino forms part of an entertainment complex in the city which includes "[[Le Galion]]" next door, the [[Supermarche Casino]] across the street and the [[City Sport Centre (Port-Gentil)|City Sport Centre]]. It opens at 10pm from Thursday to Sunday and features [[blackjack]], [[roulette]], [[poker]] and slot machines.<ref name="AuziasLabourdette2008">{{cite book|last1=Auzias|first1=Dominique|last2=Labourdette|first2=Jean-Paul|title=GABON SAO TOME ET PRINCIPE 2008: 2009 PETIT FUTE|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZIpWmWRSyQkC&pg=PA213|accessdate=10 March 2011|date=19 March 2008|publisher=Petit Futé|isbn=978-2-7469-1290-8|page=213}}</ref><ref name="Warne2003">{{cite book|last=Warne|first=Sophie|title=Gabon, São Tomé and Príncipe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wTCyVLanWZwC&pg=PA125|accessdate=10 March 2011|date=1 November 2003|publisher=Bradt Travel Guides|isbn=978-1-84162-073-2|page=125}}</ref>

