{{Infobox intangible heritage | Image = Zmijanje embroidery in BL store 2.jpg | Size = | Caption = Zmijanje embroidery in store in Banja Luka | ICH = Zmijanje embroidery | State Party = Bosnia and Herzegovina | ID = | Region = ENA | Category = | Year = 2014 | Session = 9th | Link = https://ich.unesco.org/en/RL/zmijanje-embroidery-00990 }} '''Zmijanje embroidery''' ({{lang-sr|Змијањски вез}} / {{lang|sr-Latn|Zmijanjski vez}}) is a specific technique of [[embroidery]] practised by the women of villages in area [[Zmijanje]] on mountain [[Manjača]] in [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]].
In 2014 it is included on the [[UNESCO Intangible Cultural Heritage Lists|UNESCO Representative List of the Intangible Cultural Heritage of Humanity]].<ref>http://www.unesco.org/culture/ich/en/RL/00990</ref>
